        "short_description": "Senren＊Banka is a Japanese-style visual novel produced by Yuzusoft, a Japanese developer of romance VNs. This game commemorated Yuzusoft's 10th anniversary. It won numerous awards on the year of its release in Japan for its art, music, and characters.",
        "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Senren＊Banka is a Japanese-style visual novel produced by Yuzusoft, a Japanese developer of romance VNs. <br>This game commemorated Yuzusoft's 10th anniversary. It won numerous awards on the year of its release in Japan for its art, music, and characters. <br>It was a runner-up for the 2016 Moe Game Awards, and it won the first overall ranking in Getchu's 2016 Bishoujo Game Awards.</h2><br><br>The Steam version contains English, Simplified and Traditional Chinese, and Japanese text options with Japanese voice acting. It also enjoys Steam Cloud support.<br><br><strong>Disclaimer: All characters depicted in this game are 18 years of age or older</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144400/extras/eb628eada5db150b8fcd5581bb5708f9.poster.avif?t=1752128014\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144400/extras/eb628eada5db150b8fcd5581bb5708f9.webm?t=1752128014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144400/extras/eb628eada5db150b8fcd5581bb5708f9.mp4?t=1752128014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144400/extras/dc0d3b80cfb475fa5f4574b42dab1e38.avif?t=1752128014\" width=600 height=1165 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144400/extras/abe5df13fe05397f5823931d02aa87e7.poster.avif?t=1752128014\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1144400/extras/abe5df13fe05397f5823931d02aa87e7.webm?t=1752128014\" type=\"video/webm; codec